    "description": "For this well-balanced bowl, you'll blend leeks, sweet peas, spinach and onion with garlic and ginger for warmth. Then, swirl in miso and creamy coconut yogurt for depth. Finish with a drizzle of garlicky pumpkin seed chilli oil for a gentle kick. 3 or more of your 5/day.",
